### 2. Hard Limit Relaxations
- **File**: [writer](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_narrative_write_biography.txt)

| What | Before | After |
|---|---|---|
| sub_key_data scope rule | "1-2 sentences max per item" | "NOT as standalone scenes" (no sentence limit) |
| Bridge | "1-2 sentences max" / "Maximum: 2 sentences" | "keep it brief" / "brief" |
| Scene minimum | "Minimum: 80 words per scene" | Removed |
| POV shift duration | "Max 3-4 sentences" | "3-6 sentences" |
| Anti-duplication | "Reference it in 1 sentence max" | "Reference it briefly" |

