### 3. Outline: DISTRIBUTE, Not RE-PICK
- **File**: [outline](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_narrative_outline_biography.txt)
- **Old**: `main_key_data: "Max 3 items — pick data from the SAME life_phase_covered... Less is more"`
- **New**: `"DISTRIBUTE from phase plan's main_key_data. ALL phase plan main events MUST appear. Do NOT re-pick from blueprint. Do NOT drop events."`
- DEDUP RULE → DISTRIBUTION RULE: phase plan events cannot be dropped

---

### 4. Bridge Disconnect Fix (TRANSITION RULE)
- **File**: [writer](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_narrative_write_biography.txt) OPENING section
- Added: NEVER start chapter with blind pronoun ("This caused...", "It changed...", "NÓ...")
- Must use **Explicit Noun** (preferred) or **Thematic Echo** (alternative)

---

### 5. CLOSING Enforcement (`ends_with` = final idea)
- **File**: [writer](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_narrative_write_biography.txt) CLOSING section
- **Old**: "ends_with must be WOVEN into your final paragraph"
- **New**: "ends_with is the FINAL IDEA. Do NOT add extra sentences AFTER it. Nothing comes after."

---

### 6. Hook ANCHOR → TWIST Fix (Root Cause)
**Problem**: Ch1 always opened with "Pero..." (But...) — skipping setup.

**Root cause traced through 3 layers:**

| Layer | Problem | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| **Phase plan** | Hook phase had `main_key_data: []` | Must have 2 items: ANCHOR + TWIST |
| **Outline** | Hook data was all contrast/twist, no setup | ANCHOR → TWIST order enforced |
| **Writer** | "ALREADY KNOWS" → AI assumed context | "ESTABLISH the subject's NAME or concrete fact" |

**Files changed:**
- [phase_plan](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_narrative_phase_plan_biography.txt): HOOK PHASE rule
- [outline](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_narrative_outline_biography.txt): HOOK main_key_data ANCHOR→TWIST
- [writer](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_narrative_write_biography.txt): HOOK STRUCTURE + ANTI-PATTERNS

---

### 7. Consequence Classification (SCENE TEST)
- **File**: [phase_plan](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_narrative_phase_plan_biography.txt)
- **Old**: "DIRECT CONSEQUENCES of a previous node → sub" (too aggressive, demoted "Forced to flee")
- **New**: SCENE TEST — Can the consequence be developed into its own SCENE? YES → main. NO → sub.

---

### 8. ANTI-MERGE Rule
- **File**: [phase_plan](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/prompts/system_narrative_phase_plan_biography.txt)
- Each blueprint event = one separate array item. Do NOT compress distinct events into single items.
- Protects node count accuracy → correct split decisions

---

